{"tid":141772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"96歲老婦被床蝨咬到，2天後不幸死去！","createTime":"2017-03-03T07:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T05:01:51.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b1ea12c2a2bc1b7aa1ce1400b226ba71f52e04","tid":141772,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:45:43.000Z","msg":"96歲老婦被床蝨咬到，2天後不幸死去！<br />\n<br />\n一名老婦慘遭臭蟲咬傷而死&hellip;96歲的瑪莉 (Mary Stoner) 在搬出位於賓州的照顧者黛博拉 (Deborah Butler) 的家後，沒兩天就被送到急診室，但經治療後仍不幸去世。醫師發現瑪莉身上有多處發炎以及蟲咬感染的痕跡，驗屍發現她的死因是臭蟲 (床蝨) 侵擾引發的敗血性併發症。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.towngag.com.hk/file/thumb/dd700b2a842585de2e7cc49380f14c3c-1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.towngag.com.hk%2Ffile%2Fthumb%2Fdd700b2a842585de2e7cc49380f14c3c-1600max.jpg&h=d6ef34e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是Manheim Township警方調查黛博拉的住家，結果一進去就嚇到了，因為臭蟲的肆虐比他們想像中還嚴重，棕色的蟲子爬滿了牆壁、床單跟枕頭，72歲的黛博拉也因此面臨醫療照顧疏忽的一級重罪，以及非故意過失致死的輕罪。  <br />\n廣告 瑪莉於2月22日死於醫院，正好在她搬回家後兩週。她的家人在注意到她的健康狀況急遽下降後，將她從照顧者的家帶回自家。雖然黛博拉宣稱她完全沒注意到瑪莉健康狀況有變化，警方表示死者的健康狀況是顯而易見，而且明顯需要治療。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  黛博拉的另一名照顧對象是位盲人，她說她能「感覺牠們在爬」，爬滿她全身還咬她。黛博拉在她有證照的養護之家Luckenbaugh個人養護之家關閉後，就親自在家中照顧患者。她之前的機構並沒有違反賓州公共服務部的規定。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Dailymail<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.towngag.com.hk/view3/post/6405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.towngag.com.hk%2Fview3%2Fpost%2F6405&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9e8b69a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.towngag.com.hk/view3/post/6405</a>"},{"pid":"2195fea07e9208451334b85ad62540789161254a","tid":141772,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:19:19.000Z","msg":"20後啲抵抗力需要被關注"},{"pid":"08f7e613134b52d3fc3fb2d7f3cb7565304e805e","tid":141772,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n啲仔女係唔係搏拎保險"},{"pid":"91fb3f65fe245eb8da757b6c4786d9f31fce61c0","tid":141772,"uid":59447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"她之前的機構並沒有違反賓州公共服務部的規定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ac5e94e389dde00d29cdb02c9f5152fda11290","tid":141772,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"棕色的蟲子爬滿了牆壁、床單跟枕頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d10e2cac45dcc282b1632b01f31d775848779a","tid":141772,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.moviesteve.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/they_crawl1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.moviesteve.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F06%2Fthey_crawl1.png&h=d1548e8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"338908f7bf577b252dc908314c8c2ee3b8a663f1","tid":141772,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b7426c2b6d504191292dcee5155dfe645f6207","tid":141772,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f1273add926df057cebe01ec10dd9b404529dc","tid":141772,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"好恐怖"}]}